channel.description:
[img]http://img85.imageshack.us/my.php?image=getpasserror2ev2.png[/img]The Problem is NO Longer the getPass part, it's the (name)... [br][size=1]Posted at: August 13, 2006, 06:56:05 PM[/size][hr]
[img]http://img85.imageshack.us/img85/4683/getpasserror2ev2.png[/img]The Problem is NO Longer the getPass part, it's the (name)... That is referred to as the other player's id. For Example; ::getpass beatmedown
beatmedown would be the "+name+" you are looking at.

item.title: "getpass" command problem in cilent.java
item.dc:creator: @Blazpkr Blazpkr
item.description:
@Blazpkr wrote:

OK dude the error you are getting is to do with the client.java notepad file. On some sources just called client. Ok Ive had this problem many times so its a common mistake. What you want to do is look at the errors in the black compile box. Look what they say then go on client.java file again. Press CTRL+F and the same time. And type in a bit of one of your errors find that bit and either try to correct it or delete it and if you want to put it in again find the code again and redo it. If it doesnt work by doing that i not really sure what to do as i havent been making servers long so sorry if i cannot be more help hopefully somebody else can help you:)
